Package: shareIBC
Title: Share IBC
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person('Anderson', 'Arroyo', email = 'a.arroyo@pucp.pe', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: Application of the Social Ministry at IBC Madrid created to
  allow members of the community to share job opportunities, offer their
  professional services, recycle and give away free items, request assistance
  and donate to the ministry.
